    # m "I remembered that Adine had told me that the café did deliveries as well, and not having anything else better to do, I figured I should try it out. I made my order with a quick phone call, and it wasn't long before the doorbell rang."
    m "아디네가 카페에서 배달 일도 한다고 했었고, 난 따로 할 것도 없었기에, 한 번 배달을 받아보기로 했다. 전화를 해서 배달을 시킨 뒤, 얼마 안 되어 초인종이 울렸다."

# game/adine1.rpy:32
translate Korean adine1_d60c0822:

    # c "(Well, that was quick.)"
    c "(음, 빠르네.)"

# game/adine1.rpy:39
translate Korean adine1_245dbdc1:

    # m "It just so happened that Adine herself stood in the doorway, dripping wet and with damp containers in her grip."
    m "아디네는 문 앞에 서있었다. 그녀는 물방울을 떨어트리며 양 손에 젖은 용기를 들고 있었다."

# game/adine1.rpy:61
translate Korean adine1_c084e644:

    # Ad "Oh, it's you."
    Ad "아, 당신이네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:63
translate Korean adine1_2ec83f33:

    # Ad think b "I thought they sent you away after everything that's going on."
    Ad think b "무슨 일이 있었는지 다 알고 당신을 보낸 줄 알았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:65
translate Korean adine1_ba9efa2f:

    # c "They changed their minds, so I suppose you'll be stuck with me for a little while longer."
    c "They changed their minds, so I suppose you'll be stuck with me for a little while longer."

# game/adine1.rpy:67
translate Korean adine1_c84f55d5:

    # Ad normal b "I see."
    Ad normal b "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:73
translate Korean adine1_796a7e39:

    # Ad "Oh, it's you again."
    Ad "아, 또 당신이네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:79
translate Korean adine1_7c3e6087:

    # Ad "I do remember your name, though. It was... [player_name], right?"
    Ad "하지만 전 당신의 이름을 기억하는걸요. 아마... [player_name]씨, 맞죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:80
translate Korean adine1_56d0beb3:

    # c "That's right."
    c "맞아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:83
translate Korean adine1_9d2d1212:

    # Ad "Shouldn't come as a surprise, considering you knew I deliver for the café."
    Ad "카페에서 배달 일하는 걸 아셨던 것 같아서, 놀라진 않았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:85
translate Korean adine1_56e644c8:

    # Ad "Hey."
    Ad "안녕하세요."

# game/adine1.rpy:88
translate Korean adine1_1cc03842:

    # Ad "Here's your order. Sorry, it got a little wet, but it should still be okay."
    Ad "주문하신 건 여깄어요. 죄송해요, 좀 젖긴 했지만, 그래도 이상없을 거에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:94
translate Korean adine1choice1_e6f972e8:

    # Ad "It's raining pretty heavily outside, that's all."
    Ad "밖에 좀 비가 많이 내려서 그래요."

# game/adine1.rpy:100
translate Korean adine1choice1_9a5ca63d:

    # Ad "Thanks, I was just about to ask you if I could stay for a little while. This was actually my last delivery for the day, and I live on the other side of town."
    Ad "고마워요, 들어가서 잠깐 있어도 될까하고 물어보려했었는데. 여기가 마지막 배달이고, 전 마을 반대편에 살아서요."

# game/adine1.rpy:101
translate Korean adine1choice1_be0b9602:

    # c "Of course, I couldn't let you fly back when it's this ugly outside."
    c "날씨가 저런데 당신이 날아가게 둘 순 없죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:105
translate Korean adine1choice1_8c2647a6:

    # m "I was just about to close the door in her face again when she suddenly spoke up."
    m "문을 닫으려던 참이었는데, 갑자기 그녀가 말했다."

# game/adine1.rpy:107
translate Korean adine1choice1_db4b5fa0:

    # Ad "Wait."
    Ad "잠깐만요."

# game/adine1.rpy:108
translate Korean adine1choice1_0f173ebb:

    # c "What is it?"
    c "네?"

# game/adine1.rpy:110
translate Korean adine1choice1_f8bbc1ff:

    # Ad "Do you think I could come in for a few minutes? It's raining pretty heavily outside, and this was my last delivery for the day. I actually live on the other side of town, and I don't really want to fly back in the rain."
    Ad "잠깐동안만 안에 있어도 될까요? 지금 비가 너무 많이 와서요. 이게 마지막 배달이라 집에 가야하는데, 제 집은 마을 반대편에 있어서 빗속을 뚫고 날아가기 어려울 것 같아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:117
translate Korean menadine_b2d97902:

    # Ad "Thank you."
    Ad "고마워요."

# game/adine1.rpy:126
translate Korean menadine_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/adine1.rpy:128
translate Korean menadine_544afc3c:

    # n "Without another word, I closed the door, with nothing now separating me from the delights of the slightly soggy food before me."
    n "다른 말 없이, 난 문을 닫았고, 이제 난 내 식사를 즐길 수 있게되었다. 좀 젖긴 했어도."

# game/adine1.rpy:129
translate Korean menadine_a00b0992:

    # n "I opened my container in anticipation, but what I found inside wasn't at all what I was expecting. It was noodles, with chicken and some sort of sauce."
    n "나는 기대감에 부풀어 포장을 풀었고, 내가 예상한 것과는 다르게 음식이 좀 많이 담겨있었다. 국수와 치킨, 그리고 소스."

# game/adine1.rpy:130
translate Korean menadine_07803e25:

    # n "The problem was, I hadn't ordered noodles. I rushed to the door, wondering what had gone wrong and what I had done to deserve this, but it was too late."
    n "문제는, 내가 국수는 주문하지 않았다는 것이다. 나는 황급히 문을 열어 음식이 잘못온 것 같다고 말하려고 했지만, 이미 늦어버린 후였다."

# game/adine1.rpy:131
translate Korean menadine_54475cd1:

    # n "Adine was already gone."
    n "아디네는 이미 가버렸다."

# game/adine1.rpy:156
translate Korean menadine_b01b710e:

    # Ad "Thank you!"
    Ad "고마워요!"

# game/adine1.rpy:162
translate Korean menadine_68d0fcf9:

    # Ad "Come on, don't make me fly in the rain like this. Please?"
    Ad "제발요, 절 이 빗 속에서 날게 하지 말아주세요."

# game/adine1.rpy:188
