# game/adine1.rpy:254
translate Korean menadine_e53dbbb3:

    # c "Feel right at home. I better eat this before it gets cold."
    c "집처럼 편하게 계세요. 전 식기 전에 먹어야겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:257
translate Korean menadine_f212dc62:

    # m "I sat down at the table and started eating my food while Adine decided to take a seat opposite of myself."
    m "나는 식탁에 앉아 음식을 먹기 시작했다. 아디네는 내 반대편에 앉았다."

# game/adine1.rpy:260
translate Korean menadine_58b7831b:

    # Ad "Do you like it?"
    Ad "맛은 괜찮아요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:263
translate Korean menadine_d2241b6c:

    # c "Yeah, I ordered something I knew I'd actually like this time. I didn't want to make the same mistake I did earlier today."
    c "네, 이번엔 제가 아는 걸 주문했어요. 저번처럼 같은 실수를 하긴 싫었거든요."

# game/adine1.rpy:265
translate Korean menadine_d9534b58:

    # c "Yeah, it's actually quite good."
    c "네, 꽤 맛있어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:267
translate Korean menadine_502163a4:

    # Ad "Do you have something similar where you come from?"
    Ad "당신이 살던 곳에서도 이런 걸 먹어본 적 있어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:268
translate Korean menadine_a47ef0d2:

    # c "We do. As a matter of fact, it's almost scary how close it is to what we have back home."
    c "네. 사실, 제가 살던 곳에 있던 것과 너무 비슷해서 소름끼칠 정돈데요."

# game/adine1.rpy:272
translate Korean menadine_1571c3b3:

    # Ad "Really? Maybe we all just share a similar taste."
    Ad "정말요? 아마 우리는 느끼는 맛이 비슷한 것 같아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:278
translate Korean menadine_f57b79ce:

    # Ad "At least, that's what I think."
    Ad "적어도, 전 그렇게 생각해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:282
translate Korean menadine_5727fe5d:

    # Ad "What do you mean?"
    Ad "무슨 말이에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:283
translate Korean menadine_e241a15e:

    # c "Well, don't you trace your origins back to humans in some way? I know what kind of reputation we have in your culture."
    c "음, 어찌됐거나 여러분들의 시초가 인간이라고 생각하지 않으세요? 인간이 여러분들 사이에서 어떤 이미지인지는 알고 있거든요."

# game/adine1.rpy:285
translate Korean menadine_629d7ddb:

    # Ad "That is true."
    Ad "그건 맞는 말씀이죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:286
translate Korean menadine_45ce6c6a:

    # c "Let me ask you this: Where do you think the portal you found came from? Who built it?"
    c "그럼 하나만 물어볼게요. 포탈이 어디서 왔을 거라 생각하세요? 누가 지었을까요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:288
translate Korean menadine_ef636fcf:

    # Ad "Humans did it, of course."
    Ad "물론, 인간이 지었겠죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:290
translate Korean menadine_4ab51b92:

    # c "Exactly. If you believe humans had something to do with an artifact created who knows how many years ago, it wouldn't be a stretch to think they could have also influenced you in other ways."
    c "정확해요. 인간과 몇 년 전쯤 만들어진 유물과 인간이 관련되어 있다는 걸 믿으신다면, 인간들이 여러분들에게 영향을 줄 수 있다고 생각할 수 있는 거죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:292
translate Korean menadine_9fafc86f:

    # Ad "Even something as simple as this dish? I like that idea."
    Ad "이 요리처럼 간단한 것도요? 마음에 드네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:299
translate Korean menadine_24fbdd31:

    # Ad "I thought you just did."
    Ad "저는 쓰실 줄 알았는데."

# game/adine1.rpy:302
translate Korean menadine_a0052a82:

    # c "So, what do you do when you aren't working in the restaurant? Do you have a family?"
    c "그럼, 식당에서 일할 때 말고는 뭘 하세요? 가족이 있으세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:303
translate Korean menadine_558a112a:

    # Ad "Well, most of the time I take care of my kids."
    Ad "음, 전 보통 아이들을 돌봐요."

# game/adine1.rpy:304
translate Korean menadine_77d64a46:

    # c "Oh, nice. How many children do you have?"
    c "아, 좋네요. 아이들은 몇 명이나 있으신가요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:305
translate Korean menadine_2463bcdc:

    # Ad "They aren't really my children, per se. I just take care of them."
    Ad "사실, 제 아이들은 아니에요. 그냥 돌보기만 할 뿐이죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:306
translate Korean menadine_6ab075ea:

    # c "You are more of a foster parent, then?"
    c "위탁 부모에 가깝겠네요, 그러면?"

# game/adine1.rpy:307
translate Korean menadine_4252207b:

    # Ad "Not quite. These are orphaned children I'm talking about. I just volunteer to spend some time with them, so I'm really more of a babysitter and teacher all in one."
    Ad "그렇진 않아요. 그 아이들은 고아원의 아이들이에요. 저는 그냥 봉사한다는 느낌으로 아이들과 시간을 보낼 뿐이라서, 베이비시터나 선생님에 가깝죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:309
translate Korean menadine_719209ef:

    # Ad "I can't really take them in and care for them 24/7 like a proper parent would. I'd love to, but I work far too much to be a single parent."
    Ad "진짜 부모처럼 7일 내내 24시간 동안 그 아이들을 돌봐줄 순 없어요. 그러고 싶지만, 그러기엔 제가 너무 많이 일해서..."

# game/adine1.rpy:310
translate Korean menadine_6dae616b:

    # Ad "With the amount of time I spend at the restaurant, I don't think the kids would be any better off, so I just help out whenever I can."
    Ad "제가 식당에서 많은 시간을 일하니까, 제가 아이들을 돌보는 게 나을 것 같진 않아서, 그냥 저는 시간이 날 때만 도와주고 있어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:311
translate Korean menadine_8a56387f:

    # c "That's very nice of you."
    c "정말 친절하시네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:313
translate Korean menadine_03b324fd:

    # Ad "Thanks. These kids already didn't get a very good hand in life. I just thought that if I can make even a small difference for them it'd be worth it."
    Ad "고마워요. 그 아이들은 불우한 삶을 살아왔어요. 제가 조금이라도 변화를 줄 수 있다면, 그것만으로도 가치있다 생각해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:314
translate Korean menadine_d29d4197:

    # c "I see. What about hobbies? Do you have any?"
    c "그렇군요. 취미는요? 취미는 있으세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:318
translate Korean menadine_ebf1fe4b:

    # Ad "Can I ask a question for a change?"
    Ad "제가 먼저 질문을 드려도 될까요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:328
translate Korean menadine_f8d5feb5:

    # Ad "What? Why not?"
    Ad "네? 왜 안 돼요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:329
translate Korean menadine_ac95ba08:

    # c "Just kidding. Go ahead."
    c "농담이에요. 하셔도 돼요."

# game/adine1.rpy:335
translate Korean menadine_cdd3e6f5:

    # Ad "You're silly. I like that."
    Ad "재밌네요. 마음에 들어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:338
translate Korean menadine_75906cf7:

    # Ad "Well, I don't really know much about you. Actually, I'm not sure if there is anyone here who does."
    Ad "그게, 전 당신에 대해 잘 몰라요. 그러니까 당신이 뭘 하는 사람인지도 모르구요."

# game/adine1.rpy:339
translate Korean menadine_41444a40:

    # c "What would you like to know?"
    c "뭘 알고 싶으신데요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:341
translate Korean menadine_0dce8ee6:

    # Ad "What did you do before you came here?"
    Ad "여기 오기 전에는 무슨 일을 하셨어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:346
translate Korean menadine_52e199a5:

    # c "Nothing special, really. I mean, I have my degrees, but this is the first time I did something that was actually related to them. The work I did previously was just to keep afloat."
    c "별 건 없었어요. 진짜로. 제 말은, 제가 학위는 있었지만 그 학위와 관련된 일을 하는건 이번이 처음이거든요. 제가 전에 했던 일은 그냥 빚만 안 질 정도로 했어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:348
translate Korean menadine_4b7f20ab:

    # Ad "I know what you mean."
    Ad "무슨 뜻인 지 알겠어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:353
translate Korean menadine_02e1a99e:

    # c "Nun."
    c "알바."

# game/adine1.rpy:354
translate Korean menadine_31f04825:

    # Ad "Nun? What do you mean?"
    Ad "알바요? 그게 무슨 뜻이에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:355
translate Korean menadine_939a58e1:

    # c "I mean that it's {i}nun{/i} of your business."
    c "제 말은 딩신 {i}알 바{/i} 아니라는 거죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:357
translate Korean menadine_91cd4cae:

    # Ad "Okay..."
    Ad "알았어요..."

# game/adine1.rpy:363
translate Korean menadine_d049fb42:

    # Ad "Of course it is."
    Ad "물론 그렇겠죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:366
translate Korean menadine_0cc7643e:

    # c "I suppose it's my turn again, so tell me about your hobbies."
    c "제 차례인 것 같네요. 취미 말씀해주세요."

# game/adine1.rpy:367
translate Korean menadine_cc546db3:

    # Ad "The one I enjoy most is probably flying."
    Ad "제가 즐기는 건 아마 비행같네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:368
translate Korean menadine_37f5b9ba:

    # c "Just flying?"
    c "그냥 비행이요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:370
translate Korean menadine_4b4db401:

    # Ad "Well, not {i}just{/i} flying."
    Ad "음, 물론 {i}그냥{/i} 비행은 아니죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:372
translate Korean menadine_43ec0d7d:

    # Ad "I do Aerobatics, or stunt flying. I've been doing that on and off for a couple of years now."
    Ad "에어로바틱을 해요. 스턴트 비행이라고 부르기도 하고요. 몇 년 전부터 계속 했어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:379
translate Korean menadine_f106bf6f:

    # Ad "Actually, that might not be so far from the truth."
    Ad "사실, 진실과는 좀 거리가 있겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:386
translate Korean menadine_a846bbc7:

    # Ad "That's what hobbies are for, though, right? It's just something I enjoy doing."
    Ad "하지만 그런 걸 취미라고 부르지 않나요? 그냥 제가 무언가를 즐길 수 있으니까요."

# game/adine1.rpy:390
translate Korean menadine_abbb67c9:

    # Ad "It's the practice of doing flying maneuvers like rolls, spins or loops."
    Ad "구르거나, 돌거나, 고리 모양을 만들며 기술을 연출하는 걸 말해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:392
translate Korean menadine_3a20ab9d:

    # Ad "I'm actually hoping to be part of a competition in some time."
    Ad "언젠가는 대회에서 날아보고 싶어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:399
translate Korean menadine_e2d25ad9:

    # Ad "Just because I can fly in the rain doesn't mean that I want to."
    Ad "비 속에서 날 수 있다해서 제가 날고 싶다는 건 아니에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:402
translate Korean menadine_a6751830:

    # Ad "That's what I'm trying to find out."
    Ad "저도 제가 얼마나 잘하는지 한 번 알아보고 싶어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:406
translate Korean menadine_3a15203a:

    # Ad "I suppose that depends on whether you will still be here when it takes place. It's part of a festival we hold in this town every year."
    Ad "그 때 당신이 여기 머물러 있을지 모르겠어요. 이 마을에서 매년 축제가 열리는데, 그 때 해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:409
translate Korean menadine_410ee6b4:

    # Ad "Okay, since it is my turn again, well..."
    Ad "그래서, 제 차례 같네요, 음..."

# game/adine1.rpy:411
translate Korean menadine_02d2db07:

    # Ad "This might be an unusual question, so... When they said it was a human that would be coming here, I kinda expected something a little different."
    Ad "좀 특이한 질문이긴한데, 그래서... 인간이 여기로 찾아온다고 했을 때, 전 살짝 다른 걸 기대했거든요."

# game/adine1.rpy:418
translate Korean menadine_9beac2da:

    # Ad "You know what I mean..."
    Ad "제가 뭔 말하는지는 아시잖아요..."

# game/adine1.rpy:424
translate Korean menadine_2f44ec25:

    # Ad "I'm not sure exactly, but they do say it was humans that made us who we are today. You don't seem so different from us, though."
    Ad "저도 잘 모르겠어요. 하지만 인간들이 우리를 만든 존재라고들 하거든요. 근데 사실 우리랑 크게 다른 것 같지 않아서요."

# game/adine1.rpy:427
translate Korean menadine_53f42aeb:

    # c "I know. Remy told me about some of the commonly held beliefs here."
    c "저도 알아요. 레미도 여기서 흔히 믿는 미신들을 말해줬어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:430
translate Korean menadine_ac2a2159:

    # Ad "I mean, yeah, you do look different from us, but you're not really anything like some of the things that have been said about your kind."
    Ad "제 말은, 음, 당신이 우리랑 다르게 생기긴 했지만, 알려져있던 것과는 너무나도 달라서요."

# game/adine1.rpy:431
translate Korean menadine_91928a3d:

    # c "I could say the same thing about you."
    c "그건 제 쪽도 마찬가지에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:433
translate Korean menadine_c097ab55:

    # Ad "Really?"
    Ad "정말요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:434
translate Korean menadine_93f88486:

    # c "Yeah, we have plenty of myths about dragons."
    c "네, 저희도 용에 대한 신화가 많은걸요."

# game/adine1.rpy:438
translate Korean menadine_8b9da41f:

    # Ad "Like what?"
    Ad "예를 들자면요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:442
translate Korean menadine_c21eb134:

    # c "There are just too many to list. Some of them good, some not so much."
    c "너무 많아요. 어떤 건 좋은 쪽이지만, 어떤 건 그렇게 좋지는 못하죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:444
translate Korean menadine_8abc6d5e:

    # Ad "Sounds like what we have on you, actually. Now that I see one of you right in front of me, it's almost silly what some of the myths say."
    Ad "우리랑 다를 게 없네요. 제 앞에 이렇게 인간을 실제로 보니까, 몇몇 신화는 웃겨지기까지 해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:452
translate Korean menadine_54e6a0c5:

    # c "Well, according to some, you are greedy, man-eating monsters, and also sometimes associated with evil and the apocalypse."
    c "음, 저희 신화 중 일부는, 당신은 탐욕스럽고, 식인 괴물이며, 악마나 종말과도 관련있을 거라 묘사하기도 해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:454
translate Korean menadine_b7bc313e:

    # Ad "Well, that's not very nice."
    Ad "음, 그건 별로네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:456
translate Korean menadine_fbe98f30:

    # Ad "Though to be fair, some of what we have about you isn't very nice, either."
    Ad "솔직히, 우리 신화들도 조금은 당신이 나쁘게 나오긴 해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:458
translate Korean menadine_db56dd45:

    # c "Phew, good to know you aren't vicious monsters, then."
    c "휴, 당신이 악랄한 괴물은 아니라서 다행이네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:459
translate Korean menadine_e5322ba8:

    # Ad "Oh, we can be vicious if we want to be. We just usually know better."
    Ad "아, 우리는 얼마든지 악랄해질 수 있어요. 그냥 그러지 않을 뿐이지."

# game/adine1.rpy:465
translate Korean menadine_377987b8:

    # c "They are often cited as a symbol of power and strength, but also one of wisdom, possessing an intellect that has no equal. They are noble creatures, and their depictions enjoy an almost universal appeal."
    c "힘과 권력의 상징으로 표현되기도 하고, 지혜의 상징으로서 독보적인 지능의 소유자로 표현되기도 하죠. 그들은 고귀한 생명체고, 전 세계적으로 대부분 묘사가 그래요."

# game/adine1.rpy:466
translate Korean menadine_d7e7b442:

    # Ad "I could get used to that, though it would be even nicer if it were all true."
    Ad "익숙해져야겠어요. 하지만 그게 사실이었다면 더 좋았을텐데요."

# game/adine1.rpy:468
translate Korean menadine_9fd77ad2:

    # Ad "To be honest, I don't know if it's such a good idea to generalize like that - even if it's good things you're saying about us. We're all different, you know, and not all of us are nice."
    Ad "솔직히, 그렇게 일반화하는 게 좋은 생각인지 잘 모르겠어요. 그렇게 좋게 말씀하시지만, 우리는 모두 다르고, 우리 모두가 착한 건 아니에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:470
translate Korean menadine_89aefe22:

    # c "I see."
    c "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:471
translate Korean menadine_c249e3f8:

    # Ad "But then, we have said many good things about your kind, too."
    Ad "그건 그렇지만, 우리도 인간에 대해 많이들 좋게 말해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:476
translate Korean menadine_0eb9375b:

    # c "Well, no matter what you might think about humans, I can assure you that I am in no way special or supernatural."
    c "음, 당신이 인간에 대해 어떻게 생각하는 지는 모르겠지만, 전 초자연적인 힘을 가지고 있다거나 특별하다거나 하진 않습니다."

# game/adine1.rpy:478
translate Korean menadine_a498f8f9:

    # Ad "I disagree with that."
    Ad "그건 동의할 수 없네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:479
translate Korean menadine_4e5a4202:

    # c "Why?"
    c "왜요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:481
translate Korean menadine_dc481bac:

    # Ad "You say that you aren't special, but just the fact that you're here with us right now is quite special to me and many others. Just try to see it the other way around."
    Ad "당신이 특별하지 않다고 했죠? 하지만 당신은 지금 여기 우리와 함께 있고 그것만으로도 특별하다는 거에요. 조금 다른 시선으로 바라보자구요."

# game/adine1.rpy:482
translate Korean menadine_488948a9:

    # c "You know, you have a good point."
    c "맞는 말씀이네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:483
translate Korean menadine_161c79f2:

    # Ad "What were you thinking when you first heard about us?"
    Ad "당신은 우리에 대해 처음 들었을 때 무엇을 생각하셨어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:487
translate Korean menadine_22fb7d86:

    # c "I thought it was a joke. Of course, all of that changed once I came through the portal."
    c "그냥 농담인줄 알았죠. 물론, 포탈을 지나고 나니 마음이 싹 바뀌었지만요."

# game/adine1.rpy:489
translate Korean menadine_27b32db1:

    # Ad "See, having something you've only heard about in stories turn out to be real is quite special."
    Ad "그쵸, 그렇게 들어만봤던 이야기가 눈 앞에 현실로 다가온다는 건 꽤 특별한 일이라구요."

# game/adine1.rpy:496
translate Korean menadine_aaa0f5f8:

    # c "I wasn't sure what to think about it. That is, until I got here and was standing in front of one of you. And after that, I was just rendered speechless."
    c "긴가민가 했어요. 그러니까, 여기 와서 실제로 용 앞에 서기 전까지는요. 그 뒤로는 말문이 턱 막혔어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:498
translate Korean menadine_c9851cf8:

    # Ad "Told you so. It was special for you, too!"
    Ad "말했잖아요. 그건 특별한 일이라니까요!"

# game/adine1.rpy:506
translate Korean menadine_9cf84c2e:

    # c "I thought making a discovery like this was just awesome. Many people would love to have the opportunity I had by coming here."
    c "이런 발견을 한다는 게 꽤 멋질거라 생각했어요. 많은 사람들이 이 곳에 오고 싶어했죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:508
translate Korean menadine_821be8f1:

    # Ad "See, it's not so one-sided after all, so don't be surprised if some of us feel the same way."
    Ad "그쵸, 그건 당신 세계에서만 그런 건 아니니까, 우리들이 마찬가지라도 놀랄 건 없죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:514
translate Korean menadine_827a62d3:

    # c "And it's not just the discovery of you dragons. We found a portal to an entirely different world. We still haven't figured that one out."
    c "그리고 이건 당신들 용에 대한 발견만이 아니에요. 우리는 완전히 다른 세계를 연결해주는 포탈을 찾았다고요. 어떻게 사용하는 지도 알아내지 못했고..."

# game/adine1.rpy:515
translate Korean menadine_684b625c:

    # Ad "Neither have we."
    Ad "그건 저희도 마찬가지에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:516
translate Korean menadine_5479d226:

    # c "I'm sure we'll find out soon enough."
    c "곧 찾을 수 있겠죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:520
translate Korean menadine_ef4c12fa:

    # Ad "By the way, interesting selection of books you have there. \"Draconic Desire\", \"Ixomen Sphere\" - are these yours?"
    Ad "그건 그렇고, 여기 책이 꽤 재밌어보이네요. \"엄격한 욕구\", \"익소멘 구\".. 이거 당신 건가요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:521
translate Korean menadine_304794b1:

    # c "No, they were already here when I moved in."
    c "아뇨, 여기로 왔을 때부터 있었어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:525
translate Korean menadine_173c151b:

    # Ad "Have you read any of them?"
    Ad "읽어봤어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:526
translate Korean menadine_2ad87d8f:

    # c "I did read \"Sheridan and the Scepter of Sovereignty\"."
    c "I did read \"셰리단과 제국의 왕홀\"을 읽어봤죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:527
translate Korean menadine_8752fb4f:

    # Ad "How did you like it?"
    Ad "어때요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:533
translate Korean menadine_26e8f868:

    # Ad "\"Nothing special\" is a good way to describe the entire series, actually."
    Ad "\"특별할 건 없다\"라고 말씀하시니 확실히 와닿네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:543
translate Korean menadine_43ebd9ef:

    # Ad "I see."
    Ad "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:553
translate Korean menadine_4f76bc1a:

    # Ad "I can see why."
    Ad "왜 그런지 알겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:559
translate Korean menadine_a9cad82b:

    # Ad "Oh, you've got \"Price and Prayer\". You should totally read that one."
    Ad "앗, \"대가와 기도\"도 있네요. 이건 꼭 읽어보셔야해요."

# game/adine1.rpy:560
translate Korean menadine_d98d0cd8:

    # c "You think so? Why's that?"
    c "그래요? 어떤데요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:561
translate Korean menadine_9df698e3:

    # Ad "It's not just an interesting story, it's based on true events. The author is so right when he says there's a lot we can learn from what happened back then."
    Ad "이게 그냥 흥미로운 이야기가 아니라, 실화를 기반으로 한 책이에요. 그 당시 일을 통해 배울 것이 많다고 말하는 게 너무 와닿았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:568
translate Korean menadine_089aa707:

    # Ad "It's more than just a book. I suppose it might not seem that important to someone who doesn't live here, though."
    Ad "단순한 책은 아니에요. 하지만 당신은 여기 살아보지 않았으니 그렇게 보이지 않을 수도 있겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:573
translate Korean menadine_98d1aad3:

    # Ad "Let me know when you do. I'd be interested in hearing what you have to say about it."
    Ad "언제 한 번 읽고 말해줘요. 그걸 읽고 뭘 말씀하실지 기대되네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:578
translate Korean menadine_4b7f20ab_1:

    # Ad "I know what you mean."
    Ad "무슨 뜻인지 알겠어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:581
translate Korean menadine_9e9eaf83:

    # Ad "Alright, since you asked about my family earlier, I'm going to do the same thing. Is there a Mr. or Mrs. [player_name] back home waiting for you?"
    Ad "아, 아까 제 가족에 대해 물어보셨죠? 저도 물어볼게요. [player_name]씨는 집에 기다려주는 사람이 있어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:582
translate Korean menadine_a26d4342:

    # c "No, can't say there is."
    c "아뇨, 있다고는 말하지 못하겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:584
translate Korean menadine_d16f87c9:

    # Ad "How about a potential Mr. or Mrs. [player_name], then? Are you looking to date anyone?"
    Ad "그러면 [player_name]씨의 미래에는요? 사귀는 사람 있으세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:591
translate Korean menadine_02b24bc2:

    # Ad "Come on, tell me!"
    Ad "아, 말해주세요!"

# game/adine1.rpy:595
translate Korean menadine_75d20bbd:

    # Ad "I see. Anyone on your radar, then? Someone you think is attractive?"
    Ad "그렇군요. 그러면 마음 속으로는 있어요? 뭔가 매력적인 사람이라던지?"

# game/adine1.rpy:602
translate Korean menadine_6b0e1c03:

    # Ad "Oh, it's a shame you can't be with them now, then."
    Ad "아, 그 분과 함께 있지 못해서 슬프겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:604
translate Korean menadine_d3b70432:

    # Ad "Or are you talking about someone you met here?"
    Ad "근데 말씀하시는 그 분은 여기서 만나신 건가요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:615
translate Korean tellme_98edf115:

