# game/adine1.rpy:647
translate Korean choiceb_2c403123:

    # Ad "No one at all? I don't believe you. I think you just don't want to tell me. So, who is the lucky person?"
    Ad "아무도 없다구요? 안 믿어지는데요. 그냥 저한테 말해주기 싫은가보네요. 그러면, 누가 행운아가 되려나?"

