# game/adine1.rpy:697
translate Korean nextsc_e17aa8de:

    # c "I'm not sure how many questions that was, but I'm sure it's not your turn anymore."
    c "질문을 몇개나 하셨는지는 모르겠지만, 확실히 이제 당신 차례는 아닌 것 같네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:701
translate Korean nextsc_fe09c854:

    # Ad "Are we even still playing this game?"
    Ad "그 게임 아직도 하고 있던거에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:708
translate Korean nextsc_98f9c271:

    # Ad "That's true. You seem to be enjoying it, though."
    Ad "그건 맞는 말이네요. 하지만 당신도 즐기고 있었는걸요."

# game/adine1.rpy:714
translate Korean nextsc_9603eefb:

    # Ad "You and me both."
    Ad "우리 둘 다 재미삼아 하는거죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:719
translate Korean nextsc_45100626:

    # Ad "Well, go ahead, then."
