# game/adine1.rpy:721
translate Korean nextsc_e5da73be:

    # c "You know, why don't we make this a little more interesting while we're at it?"
    c "이건 어때요, 하는 김에 좀 더 재밌게 해보는 건 어때요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:723
translate Korean nextsc_4a6d854a:

    # Ad "What do you suggest?"
    Ad "어떻게요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:724
translate Korean nextsc_27c37c55:

    # c "Truth or dare."
    c "진실게임이죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:726
translate Korean nextsc_8f23b6c8:

    # Ad "What's that?"
    Ad "그게 뭔데요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:727
translate Korean nextsc_20ec6614:

    # c "We continue asking questions, but if one of us doesn't want to answer the question, we have to do something the other person tells us to."
    c "질문을 서로 주고받다가, 한 쪽이 질문에 대답하기 싫어하면, 다른 한 쪽이 시키는 일을 해야하는 거죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:729
translate Korean nextsc_bf87ec10:

    # Ad "I don't even know what kind of dare I would make you do."
    Ad "전 당신에게 뭘 시켜야할 지도 모르는 걸요."

# game/adine1.rpy:730
translate Korean nextsc_4453a933:

    # c "It could be something that would make me uncomfortable, or something you'd like to see me do."
    c "그냥 제가 하기 불편한 일이라던지, 당신이 보고 싶은 걸 시켜도 되고요."

# game/adine1.rpy:734
translate Korean nextsc_0532a010:

    # Ad "Anything?"
    Ad "아무거나요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:735
translate Korean nextsc_206795eb:

    # c "Well, keep in mind that revenge might be coming quicker than you think, so don't ask someone for anything you wouldn't do yourself."
    c "뭐, 복수는 생각보다 빨리 찾아온다는 건 잊지 마세요. 당신이 제게 시킨 걸 당신이 하게 될 수도 있으니."

# game/adine1.rpy:739
translate Korean nextsc_b0e643f3:

    # Ad "Got it. So, who's first?"
    Ad "알았어요. 그래서, 누가 먼저죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:740
translate Korean nextsc_24285aa7:

    # c "You asked the last few questions, so it's only fair if I start."
    c "당신이 아까 저한테 질문을 여러 개 하셨으니, 제가 먼저 시작하는 게 공평하겠죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:744
translate Korean nextsc_58abfc7c:

    # Ad "Alright."
    Ad "알았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:752
translate Korean nextsc_deda5e50:

    # Ad "Probably my sides."
    Ad "옆구리같네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:754
translate Korean nextsc_4e50fccb:

    # c "Good to know."
    c "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:756
translate Korean nextsc_6c279b9e:

    # Ad "You wouldn't misuse that knowledge, would you?"
    Ad "그거 악용하진 않으시겠죠, 그쵸?"

# game/adine1.rpy:757
translate Korean nextsc_a59f8f81:

    # c "Of course not."
    c "물론 아니죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:761
translate Korean nextsc_d40811d3:

    # Ad "I don't really keep secrets."
    Ad "전 비밀같은 게 없어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:762
translate Korean nextsc_bc038d06:

    # c "That's not a real answer."
    c "그건 대답이 아니잖아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:763
translate Korean nextsc_a3e8b670:

    # Ad "But it's the truth."
    Ad "하지만 진짜인걸요."

# game/adine1.rpy:764
translate Korean nextsc_87f87efc:

    # c "You know, you aren't very good at this game."
    c "이 게임 잘 못하시는 것 같네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:766
translate Korean nextsc_a0221976:

    # Ad "Hey, it's my first time."
    Ad "이익, 처음하는 거잖아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:767
translate Korean nextsc_5101fbef:

    # c "Don't worry about it."
    c "걱정은 하지 마세요."

# game/adine1.rpy:773
translate Korean nextsc_8a18e93a:

    # Ad "Hmm, let me think..."
    Ad "흠, 잠시만요..."

# game/adine1.rpy:775
translate Korean nextsc_f0510f43:

    # Ad "There was this one time when I was still a teenager. I was messing around and wanted to try out a new flying maneuver: a barrel roll. Needless to say, it ended badly."
    Ad "제가 10대였을 때 하나 있었네요. 빈둥거리고 있었는데, 갑자기 비행 기술 하나를 해보고 싶었어요. 배럴 롤이죠. 말할 필요도 없이, 안 좋게 끝났구요."

# game/adine1.rpy:776
translate Korean nextsc_b917eced:

    # c "I guess you didn't succeed, then?"
    c "성공은 못했다는 말씀이시겠네요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:777
translate Korean nextsc_895e7591:

    # Ad "No, the roll itself went fine, but I lost control after that and plunged right to the ground."
    Ad "아뇨, 도는 것까지는 성공했는데, 균형을 잃고 땅으로 고꾸라졌죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:778
translate Korean nextsc_b2517d74:

    # c "Oh, were you hurt?"
    c "앗, 다치셨나요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:780
translate Korean nextsc_54608f68:

    # Ad "No, luckily I wasn't too high when I did it, and there was a great puddle of mud on the ground right where I landed. Of course all my friends were there to see it."
    Ad "아뇨, 다행히도 그 정도로 높지는 않았어요. 게다가 제가 떨어진 곳에 진흙 웅덩이가 있었죠. 하지만 제 친구들이 그걸 다 봤구요."

# game/adine1.rpy:781
translate Korean nextsc_57d8dcd9:

    # c "That wasn't enough to stop you from ever trying again?"
    c "그런 일을 겪고도 포기는 하지 않으셨네요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:783
translate Korean nextsc_818b4ba1:

    # Ad "No. If anything, it only made me want to try harder."
    Ad "뭐가 됐든, 그 일은 제가 더 열심히 하게 된 계기였어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:785
translate Korean nextsc_1b02c93b:

    # Ad "Since it is my turn now: What is your greatest wish?"
    Ad "그럼 이제 제 차례네요. 소원이 뭐에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:790
translate Korean nextsc_c00b79d5:

    # c "More than anything, I'd want there to be peace on Earth."
    c "다른 것보다도, 지구 평화가 이루어졌으면 좋겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:791
translate Korean nextsc_24edf6f0:

    # Ad "That is an honorable wish, [player_name]."
    Ad "그건 훌륭한 소원이네요, [player_name]씨."

# game/adine1.rpy:797
translate Korean nextsc_646ac1a5:

    # Ad "That seems to be a very personal wish, [player_name]."
    Ad "그거 엄청 개인적인 바람이네요, [player_name]씨."

# game/adine1.rpy:804
translate Korean nextsc_de415d5c:

    # c "Be rich and have the freedom to do what I want to, whenever I want to."
    c "부자가 돼서 언제나 어디서든 자유를 누리는 게 제 소원이에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:806
translate Korean nextsc_43ebd9ef:

    # Ad "I see."
    Ad "그렇군."

# game/adine1.rpy:812
translate Korean nextsc_416efc12:

    # c "Okay, my turn."
    c "좋아요, 제 차례네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:819
translate Korean nextsc_2ebf59c9:

    # Ad "Invisible, huh?"
    Ad "투명하게요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:820
translate Korean nextsc_bc0926e9:

    # Ad "That's a hard one. I mean, no one would see my flying then, and I do want people to see that."
    Ad "어려운 질문이네요. 그러니까, 전 사람들이 제가 비행하는 걸 봤으면 좋겠는데, 그렇게 되면 아무도 제가 나는 걸 보지 못하잖아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:821
translate Korean nextsc_5b659cad:

    # c "Well, with this question it's more about what you would do if you had the opportunity to do something without getting caught, like something mischievous or criminal."
    c "음, 어디로 잡혀가지 않고 그런 짓을 할 수 있는 기회가 생긴다면, 뭐든지 할 수 있는 것 아니겠어요? 짓궃은 장난이라던지, 범죄라던지."

# game/adine1.rpy:823
translate Korean nextsc_d89cde73:

    # Ad "Oh, I know what I would do. I'd check out the building they found along with the portal."
    Ad "아, 뭘 하고 싶은 지 떠올랐어요. 포탈이 있는 건물로 찾아가볼래요."

# game/adine1.rpy:824
translate Korean nextsc_1531db24:

    # c "What building?"
    c "무슨 빌딩이요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:825
translate Korean nextsc_a70918ca:

    # Ad "Didn't you hear about that? They found a whole building along with the portal."
    Ad "못 들으셨어요? 포탈이 있는 건물을 찾았대요."

# game/adine1.rpy:826
translate Korean nextsc_e950f342:

    # Ad "It's actually underground, and they have it heavily guarded while a team of archaeologists works on it. I think it might contain many secrets and answers about the portal and where it came from."
    Ad "지하에 있고, 고고학자들이 작업하느라 경비가 삼엄해졌어요. 포탈이 어디서 왔는지, 그리고 포탈에 대해서 많은 비밀이 숨겨져있을 거에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:827
translate Korean nextsc_81939529:

    # c "Interesting. I think I'd like to check that out as well."
    c "흥미롭네요. 저도 한 번 확인해봐야겠네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:830
translate Korean nextsc_e306f303:

    # Ad "No, absolutely not."
    Ad "아뇨, 절대요."

# game/adine1.rpy:831
translate Korean nextsc_73c2fcc2:

    # c "Why not?"
    c "왜 그렇죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:832
translate Korean nextsc_6507f194:

    # Ad "Well, I do have some ideas of what might happen afterwards, but even if what I think isn't true, I'm not afraid of the unknown."
    Ad "음, 죽고 나면 무슨 일이 벌어질 지 생각은 해 본 적이 있긴 하지만, 실제로 안 그럴 수도 있으니까요. 전 미지에 대해 두려워하지 않아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:834
translate Korean nextsc_c1901d4d:

    # Ad "In some sort of twisted way, I'm actually kinda curious to find out what it'll be like when it's all over."
    Ad "사실 좀 꼬아서 생각해보니, 모든 것이 끝난 뒤에는 어떤 모습일 지 궁금하네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:840
translate Korean nextsc_dace38e7:

    # Ad "Aren't you curious as well?"
    Ad "궁금하지 않으세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:841
translate Korean nextsc_11a66161:

    # c "Not this curious."
    c "그렇게 궁금하진 않아요."

# game/adine1.rpy:842
translate Korean nextsc_43ebd9ef_1:

    # Ad "I see."
    Ad "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:848
translate Korean nextsc_43ebd9ef_2:

    # Ad "I see."
    Ad "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:854
translate Korean nextsc_da6029a2:

    # Ad "That's not funny, [player_name]."
    Ad "재미없거든요, [player_name]씨."

# game/adine1.rpy:860
translate Korean nextsc_ff57023e:

    # Ad "Well, I wouldn't really call it a flaw, but if I could change one thing, it would probably be these stripes on my muzzle."
    Ad "음, 전 이게 단점인 것 같지는 않는데, 하나만 바꿀 수 있다면, 제 주둥이에 줄무늬를 바꾸고 싶네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:862
translate Korean nextsc_7bbf2eae:

    # Ad "I don't like them very much."
    Ad "전 별로 마음에 들지 않거든요."

# game/adine1.rpy:865
translate Korean nextsc_08e5ce63:

    # Ad "No matter if people like them or not, they always stand out. That's what I don't like."
    Ad "사람들이 좋아하든 말든, 항상 눈에 보인다구요. 그래서 마음에 들지 않는 거에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:871
translate Korean nextsc_7b61b183:

    # Ad "I know they aren't pretty. You don't have to repeat what I just said."
    Ad "이쁘지 않다는 건 알아요. 굳이 그걸 한 번 더 말해주셔야겠어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:877
translate Korean nextsc_27e1283c:

    # Ad "But then you aren't the one who's supposed to answer the question."
    Ad "굳이 대답해주지 않으셔도 돼요."

# game/adine1.rpy:879
translate Korean nextsc_3d75357b:

    # Ad "If you knew the world was about to end, what would you do?"
    Ad "세상이 곧 멸망한다면, 당신은 뭘 하시겠어요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:884
translate Korean nextsc_0b95e538:

    # Ad "Going out with a bang, huh?"
    Ad "신나게 논다는 거죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:895
translate Korean nextsc_375c54ad:

    # Ad "An optimist until the very end. I like that."
    Ad "마지막까지도 긍정적으로. 마음에 들어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:905
translate Korean nextsc_c11e0ee0:

    # Ad "That would be quite a show, huh?"
    Ad "꽤 볼 만한 장관이겠죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:915
translate Korean nextsc_aa2237bc:

    # Ad "I'm not sure if I could do that. I don't like tight, enclosed spaces."
    Ad "전 그럴 수 있을지 모르겠어요. 전 빡빡하고 밀폐된 공간은 싫어해서."

# game/adine1.rpy:927
translate Korean nextsc_e3afd84b:

    # Ad "That's a very difficult question, you know."
    Ad "그건 좀 어려운 질문이네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:929
translate Korean nextsc_d022c5bd:

    # Ad "Of course I'd love to visit - maybe as some sort of vacation. But if you're talking about permanently, I'm not sure if I could just pack up and leave everything behind just like that."
    Ad "물론 휴가처럼 갔다오는 거라면 환영이죠. 하지만 영원히를 말씀하시는 거라면, 모든 걸 두고 갈 수 있을지 잘 모르겠어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:932
translate Korean nextsc_b8fb304d:

    # Ad "Oh my..."
    Ad "앗..."

# game/adine1.rpy:934
translate Korean nextsc_2355e57c:

    # Ad "..."
    Ad "..."

# game/adine1.rpy:935
translate Korean nextsc_a77509ab:

    # Ad "I think it might be time for a dare now."
    Ad "벌칙을 받아야할 것 같네요."

# game/adine1.rpy:936
translate Korean nextsc_86148265:

    # c "Alright."
    c "그래요."

# game/adine1.rpy:942
translate Korean nextsc_0268ca80:

    # Ad "Just that? That's not very hard."
    Ad "겨우 그거에요? 그렇게 어렵진 않은데."

# game/adine1.rpy:943
translate Korean nextsc_dc9a1cef:

    # c "I thought I'd go easy on you, since it is your first time and all."
    c "처음이시니까, 쉽게쉽게 가야죠."

# game/adine1.rpy:944
translate Korean nextsc_43ebd9ef_3:

    # Ad "I see."
    Ad "알았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:953
translate Korean nextsc_bfaeb6df:

    # Ad "There. Satisfied?"
    Ad "됐어요. 만족하세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:955
translate Korean nextsc_5ce0ffef:

    # c "Definitely."
    c "그럼요."

# game/adine1.rpy:974
translate Korean nextsc_b8834e95:

    # s "You got Adine to remove her headgear!"
    s "아디네의 헤드기어를 제거했습니다!"

# game/adine1.rpy:978
translate Korean nextsc_5c7f4389:

    # s "You got Adine to remove her headgear. Wow."
    s "아디네의 헤드기어를 제거했습니다. 우와."

# game/adine1.rpy:982
translate Korean nextsc_890abada:

    # s "You got Adine to remove her headgear. Don't let it go to your head."
    s "아디네의 헤드기어를 제거했습니다. 그렇다고 당신이 쓰진 마시고요."

# game/adine1.rpy:987
translate Korean nextsc_93f9d835:

    # Ad "That's your dare?"
    Ad "그걸 원하세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:988
translate Korean nextsc_c0334108:

    # c "Yep."
    c "네."

# game/adine1.rpy:989
translate Korean nextsc_2355e57c_1:

    # Ad "..."
    Ad "..."

# game/adine1.rpy:991
translate Korean nextsc_9e2d907e:

    # Ad "Alright, whatever. I'll do it."
    Ad "알았어요, 뭐 어때. 할게요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1000
translate Korean nextsc_7b0e0bd9:

    # Ad "There, I did it. Satisfied?"
    Ad "자요, 했어요. 만족하세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:1002
translate Korean nextsc_5ce0ffef_1:

    # c "Definitely."
    c "그럼요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1007
translate Korean nextsc_989cc9bb:

    # Ad "Is that all?"
    Ad "그게 다에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:1008
translate Korean nextsc_38babdee:

    # c "You can find one in the pantry."
    c "저기 수납장에 하나 있을거에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1010
translate Korean nextsc_58abfc7c_1:

    # Ad "Alright."
    Ad "알았어요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1015
translate Korean nextsc_e78a619c:

    # Ad "So, should I just take a bite out of this one?"
    Ad "그래서, 이거 한 입만 베어물면 되는 거죠?"

# game/adine1.rpy:1016
translate Korean nextsc_d88b5013:

    # c "That's your dare."
    c "그게 벌칙이에요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1017
translate Korean nextsc_14ef9c1b:

    # Ad "If you say so..."
    Ad "그렇게 말하신다면..."

# game/adine1.rpy:1022
translate Korean nextsc_7711fd6d:

    # c "(She didn't even peel it or anything...)"
    c "(껍질도 안 벗기고...)"

# game/adine1.rpy:1027
translate Korean nextsc_0950e22e:

    # Ad "I'm not sure what's so special about that."
    Ad "이게 그렇게 특별하다거나 그런 건 아닌 것 같은데요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1028
translate Korean nextsc_e8bc5fde:

    # c "You didn't mind at all?"
    c "아무 것도 안 느껴지세요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:1030
translate Korean nextsc_9270e653:

    # Ad "Not a bit."
    Ad "조금도요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1032
translate Korean nextsc_d19f855d:

    # c "..."
    c "..."

# game/adine1.rpy:1033
translate Korean nextsc_89aefe22:

    # c "I see."
    c "그렇군요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1038
translate Korean nextsc_ef602e3b:

    # Ad "Is that your question, or is that already a dare?"
    Ad "그거 질문이에요, 아니면 그거 자체로 벌칙인거에요?"

# game/adine1.rpy:1039
translate Korean nextsc_8bc84341:

    # c "A question. I just couldn't think of anything better."
    c "질문이죠. 더 나은 게 떠오르지 않아서요."

# game/adine1.rpy:1041
translate Korean nextsc_30f9f005:

    # Ad "Well, then my answer would be no. I don't kiss just anyone, you know."
    Ad "뭐, 제 대답은 아니다 겠네요. 전 누구에게도 키스해본 적이 없거든."

# game/adine1.rpy:1043
translate Korean nextsc_5eb2273d:

